  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: b1c3cae70ad8d9641a4b5be915b33736, type: 3}
  m_Name: Lamp3_long2
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "Then there was this guy. I don\u2019t know his name. He looked like the
      kind of guy who would make a bad decision and then act surprised about it.
      He was holding a normal lamp. Not me, another lamp. Very basic lamp. Honestly,
      kind of ugly, but I don\u2019t like judging other lamps."
  - speakerName: Lamp
    portrait: {fileID: 0}
    text: "So I was looking at him, and I thought, okay, maybe he is going to clean
      the lamp. Maybe he is going to sell the lamp. Maybe he is just taking the lamp
      for a walk. I don\u2019t know human activities. Humans do weird stuff all the
      time, specially kids"
